LAVA_BUCKET.debuff: Every round, EVERY item takes 1 fire damage

BELL.description: Stuns an item for one until the end of next combat phase

STONECUTTER.description:
Raises an item's ATK by +1 at the cost of -1 DEF and -1 HP.
If the item is already at 1 HP it will die!
STONECUTTER.flavor: Strong enough to cut stone, but not my abs of steel!

GRINDSTONE.description: Removes an enchantment off any item on the board.
GRINDSTONE.flavor: Strong enough to cut stone, but not these abs of steel!

COMPOSTER.description:
If your opponent has any item which can be composted,
This insta-kills it.

ENDER_CHEST.description: Swap the positions of two items
